<h1>Add DJs to broadcast to your station</h1>

<p>
Go to the <%= link_to "DJ management page", djs_path %>.
</p>

<%= image_tag "guides/add_dj_scrot.png", class: "screenshot" %>
<p>
Enter the email and username for the DJ you want to add to your station. They will receive an email from info@streampusher.com, containing instructions on how to login.
Their password will be automatically generated, they should change it to one of their choosing after logging in.
</p>

<p>
This user will be able to login through their streaming client to your station at anytime.
</p>

<p>
Feel free to direct them to the <a href="/broadcasting_help">broadcasting help page</a> if they require assistance in streaming.
</p>
